scripts/unity/unity-assetbundle-builder/Library\PackageCache\com.unity.render-pipelines.universal@12.1.15\Documentation~\lit-shader.md:3:The Lit Shader lets you render real-world surfaces like stone, wood, glass, plastic, and metals in photo-realistic quality. Your light levels and reflections look lifelike and react properly across various lighting conditions, for example bright sunlight, or a dark cave. This Shader uses the most computationally heavy [shading model](shading-model.md) in the Universal Render Pipeline (URP).
