scripts/unity/unity-assetbundle-builder/Library\PackageCache\com.unity.render-pipelines.universal@12.1.15\Documentation~\upgrade-lwrp-to-urp.md:62:URP version 7.x supports both [Post Processing Stack v2 (PPv2) and its own integrated post-processing solution](https://docs.unity3d.com/Packages/com.unity.render-pipelines.universal@7.4/manual/integration-with-post-processing.html). If you have the Post Processing Version 2 package installed in your Project and you want to use URP's integrated post-processing solution, you need to delete the Post Processing Stack v2 package before you install URP into your Project. When you have installed URP, you can then recreate your post-processing effects.
