scripts/unity/unity-assetbundle-builder/Library\PackageCache\com.unity.render-pipelines.universal@12.1.15\Documentation~\rendering-to-the-same-render-target.md:3:In the Universal Render Pipeline (URP), multiple [Base Cameras](camera-types-and-render-type.md#base-camera) or [Camera Stacks](camera-stacking.md) can render to the same render target. This allows you to create effects such as split screen rendering.
